Write a program to print a Diamond Pattern of asterisks based on an input n.

SOLUTION:

n = int(input("Enter n value: "))
for i in range(1, n + 1):
    row = ""
    for j in range(n - i):
        row = row + " "
    for k in range(i):
        row = row + "* "
    print(row)
for i in range(n - 1, 0, -1):
    row = ""
    for j in range(n - i):
        row = row + " "
    for k in range(i):
        row = row + "* "
    print(row)
